Package pl.myrecipebasket.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Category
    Object Category represents a category of meals, dishes, food occasions etc., to which a Recipe can be assigned to and by which a Recipe can be described by.
    Comment
    Object Comment represents a message that can be left by User who wants to share his/hers opinion about particular Recipe with other Users.
    Image
    Object Image represents an image of a dish prepared according to a Recipe and is attached to a Comment by User

    An Image has: name - file name (e.g.
    Recipe
    Object Recipe represents a recipe placed on an external web site that User finds worth storing for later use.
    Role
    Object Role represents an authorization level that can be assigned to a User and defines what sort of actions User is allowed to undertake within MyRecipeBasket environment.
    User
    Object User represents a person who created an account in MyRecipeBasket application and is using it to store and share links to recipes found on some external web sites.
    Vote
    Object Vote represents User's opinion about particular Recipe, which can be positive or negative.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    CategoryType
    Object CategoryType represents a type that is used to describe Category and which distinguish Categories that have been provided in application from those created by User.
    VoteType
    Object VoteType represents a type that is used to describe Votes and which distinguish Votes that were left by Users who liked particular Recipe from those which were left by Users who didn't like it.
